name: Basic JADer StAtus.
description:
Become a JADer! Basic JADer StAtus gives you the great feeling of donation for great causes.
Your dollar will be donated for:
- Saving life in Africa
- Help young kids and teens with their AIDS.
- Feeding poor people all around the world
And much more!

Just-A-Dollar, that's all what they ask.


After you donate your dollar, you'll get an confirmation email with your JAD stAtus.


Want to donate more? Become a Silver JADer.
